import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react";
import { Col, Row, Container, Form } from "react-bootstrap";
const Login = () => {

  return (
    <Container style={{ margin: 10, justifyContent: "center", alignItems: "center" }}>

        <Row>
          <Col className="row justify-content-center">
            Lists
          </Col>
        </Row>

          <Row>

            <Col>
              <input
                type="text"
                class="form-control"
                style={{
                  border: "solid",
                  borderWidth: "1.5px",
                  borderColor: "#FFA052",
                  borderRadius: 5,
                  width: 250,
                  height: 30,
                  padding: 3,
                  fontSize: 16,
                  outline: 0
                }}
                placeholder="Usuário"
              />
            </Col>
          </Row>

          <Row>
            <Col>
              <input
                style={{
                  marginTop: 10,
                  border: "solid",
                  borderWidth: "1.5px",
                  borderColor: "#FFA052",
                  borderRadius: 5,
                  width: 250,
                  height: 30,
                  padding: 3,
                  fontSize: 16,
                  outline: 0
                }}
                placeholder="Senha"
              />
            </Col>
          </Row>

          <Row>
            <Col>
              <button
                style={{
                  marginTop: 10,
                  border: "none",
                  backgroundColor: "#FF5252",
                  color: "white",
                  borderRadius: 10,
                  width: 200,
                  height: 50,
                  alignItems: "center",
                  justifyContent: "center",
                  fontSize: 16,
                }}
              >Vamos lá</button>
            </Col>
          </Row>


    </Container>
  )

}

export default Login;
